1
00:00:42,840 --> 00:00:44,280
Excuse me

2
00:00:44,280 --> 00:00:46,119
Is Mr. Zhu Yihai here?

3
00:00:46,479 --> 00:00:48,039
Brother Zhu helped me out the other day

4
00:00:48,520 --> 00:00:50,000
I came especially to thank him

5
00:00:51,960 --> 00:00:53,679
Room 302 has the answer you want

6
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:54,719
Jingjing

7
00:00:55,119 --> 00:00:56,479
Coming, coming

8
00:00:58,039 --> 00:00:59,039
In such a hurry

9
00:01:03,399 --> 00:01:04,840
Playing hard to get, huh

10
00:01:09,079 --> 00:01:09,879
Jingjing

11
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:14,560
Jiao Jing

12
00:01:16,359 --> 00:01:16,799
Jiao

13
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:26,239
Dahai

14
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,519
I'm taking Jiao Jing with me

15
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:28,480
See you at the usual spot

16
00:01:29,319 --> 00:01:30,680
What's the rush?

17
00:01:33,959 --> 00:01:35,079
Wait, it's you?

18
00:01:35,599 --> 00:01:36,319
What?

19
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:37,640
Am I not good enough?

20
00:01:38,519 --> 00:01:39,760
Nothing wrong with that

21
00:01:40,439 --> 00:01:41,480
It's just...

22
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:42,439
I didn't expect it, that's all

23
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:44,879
Isn't it cold outside?

24
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,760
Wearing so little

25
00:01:49,239 --> 00:01:50,560
These muscles of yours

26
00:01:52,079 --> 00:01:53,760
You really worked them out well

27
00:01:55,079 --> 00:01:56,239
This tattoo

28
00:01:57,480 --> 00:01:59,319
So manly

29
00:01:59,319 --> 00:02:00,120
Of course

30
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,640
I'm a badass, you know

31
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:12,199
You badasses' tattoos

32
00:02:12,199 --> 00:02:13,439
are all stick-ons, aren't they?

33
00:02:13,639 --> 00:02:14,240
Enough.

34
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,639
Don't worry if mine's a stick-on or not.

35
00:02:15,639 --> 00:02:16,840
I came today to tell you

36
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,000
stay away from Brother Hai.

37
00:02:20,599 --> 00:02:21,719
Xiong Dali.

38
00:02:23,319 --> 00:02:24,120
What?

39
00:02:25,439 --> 00:02:26,360
You trying to scare me?

40
00:02:27,039 --> 00:02:28,680
Yeah, I'm scaring you.

41
00:02:29,199 --> 00:02:30,840
Staying up in the middle of the night,

42
00:02:31,719 --> 00:02:33,240
just to scare a woman like me.

43
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:34,479
Xiong Dali,

44
00:02:34,719 --> 00:02:36,120
I thought you were a real man.

45
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:39,159
This is all you've got?

46
00:02:39,879 --> 00:02:40,240
You...

47
00:02:40,719 --> 00:02:42,000
You think I won't beat you up?

48
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:43,360
Oh-ho.

49
00:02:44,159 --> 00:02:45,360
That tough, huh?

50
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:47,400
Come on, hit me, hit me.

51
00:02:48,719 --> 00:02:49,680
Xiong Dali,

52
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:52,240
you can't control Zhu Yihai,

53
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,560
so you come after me?

54
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:55,120
Aren't you something.

55
00:02:55,879 --> 00:02:57,000
Don't push me.

56
00:02:57,439 --> 00:02:58,199
Push you?

57
00:02:59,639 --> 00:03:00,400
As if you're worth it.

58
00:03:02,159 --> 00:03:02,599
Fine.

59
00:03:02,919 --> 00:03:03,800
As long as you know.

60
00:03:06,479 --> 00:03:07,039
Just wait.

61
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:10,120
Xiong Dali,

62
00:03:10,439 --> 00:03:11,919
if you've really got the guts,

63
00:03:11,919 --> 00:03:13,080
make sure Zhu Yihai never sees me

64
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,280
for the rest of his life.

65
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,439
Are you a real man or not?

66
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:16,919
You asked for this.

67
00:03:20,039 --> 00:03:21,280
The usual spot.

68
00:03:25,719 --> 00:03:26,479
Freezing to death.

69
00:03:32,439 --> 00:03:34,400
Weren't you off doing karaoke with Jiao Jing?

70
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:36,280
What, not so OK anymore?

71
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:39,000
You think Jiao Jing and I are for real?

72
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:41,120
I was just acting.

73
00:03:41,599 --> 00:03:42,960
Turns out Jiao Jing didn't play along,

74
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:44,520
but Dali bought it completely.

75
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,039
What?

76
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:47,560
What happened?

77
00:03:47,919 --> 00:03:48,800
Something's gone down.

78
00:03:49,439 --> 00:03:50,199
Take a look.

79
00:03:51,319 --> 00:03:52,120
What is this?

80
00:03:53,439 --> 00:03:55,000
Xiong Dali kidnapped someone.

81
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:57,120
Has he lost his mind?

82
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:59,240
He better not do anything stupid.

83
00:04:00,319 --> 00:04:01,199
Because if he does,

84
00:04:01,759 --> 00:04:02,719
it could end up being, you know what.

85
00:04:02,719 --> 00:04:03,639
What "you know what"?

86
00:04:03,879 --> 00:04:04,919
The death penalty.

87
00:04:04,919 --> 00:04:05,520
What?

88
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:06,680
That serious?

89
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,039
Straight to the death penalty.

90
00:04:09,039 --> 00:04:10,080
Damn.

91
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:12,199
I could hear you shouting from the back kitchen.

92
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,439
Hurry up and find Dali

93
00:04:15,439 --> 00:04:16,120
before he does anything stupid.

94
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:16,600
Hey, wait,

95
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:18,040
where's the usual spot?

96
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:20,839
I sure as hell don't know.

97
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,279
Where is it?

98
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:24,240
I don't know either.

99
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,240
Is it that place?

100
00:04:31,279 --> 00:04:32,480
I just got off the plane.

101
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,600
I'll handle the Zhu Yihai situation.

102
00:04:35,279 --> 00:04:35,839
What?

103
00:04:36,439 --> 00:04:38,600
You let him get the Aimin Street Agreement?

104
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:41,199
You're really losing it in your old age.

105
00:04:41,199 --> 00:04:42,759
From now on, factory matters,

106
00:04:42,759 --> 00:04:44,360
don't go making decisions on your own.

107
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,360
I'll handle them.

108
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:54,079
No need to take some things too seriously.

109
00:04:57,839 --> 00:04:58,480
Brother Xiong,

110
00:04:59,319 --> 00:05:00,480
I can give you what you want.

111
00:05:03,519 --> 00:05:04,279
Let me tell you,

112
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:06,120
that act doesn't work on me.

113
00:05:06,319 --> 00:05:07,319
Stay away from Brother Hai.

114
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,439
Don't think I don't know what you're up to.

115
00:05:09,439 --> 00:05:10,240
Xiong Dali,

116
00:05:10,439 --> 00:05:12,199
do you know kidnapping is against the law?

117
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:13,560
Even if it is,

118
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,040
I can't let you hurt Brother Hai.

119
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,160
Is he worth it?

120
00:05:17,439 --> 00:05:18,319
For Brother Hai,

121
00:05:18,319 --> 00:05:19,680
I'd do anything.

122
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:31,920
Section Chief Dao

123
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,759
Want me to chase Xiong Dali off?

124
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:36,639
His dad ran off with some woman a while back

125
00:05:36,639 --> 00:05:37,959
leaving him and his mom behind.

126
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,319
And because of it, his mom

127
00:05:39,319 --> 00:05:40,959
ended up dying on the job.

128
00:05:41,439 --> 00:05:42,759
If that happened to you,

129
00:05:42,879 --> 00:05:43,800
would I chase you off?

130
00:05:44,800 --> 00:05:46,120
So what's he after, then?

131
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:49,680
His dad took all the money when he left.

132
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:50,920
He doesn't even have money for the burial.

133
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:51,879
What do you think he's after?

134
00:05:52,399 --> 00:05:54,040
You can lend to him if you want, I won't.

135
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,360
A fish rots from the head,

136
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,399
he's probably no good either.

137
00:06:01,399 --> 00:06:02,720
You bunch...

138
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,399
Get up.

139
00:06:03,399 --> 00:06:03,920
Get up.

140
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:04,600
Dali.

141
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:09,839
Take this.

142
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:12,319
If you're helping me,

143
00:06:12,519 --> 00:06:13,240
I don't have any money.

144
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,519
Just take it.

145
00:06:14,839 --> 00:06:15,959
Don't make me beat you up.

146
00:06:19,199 --> 00:06:20,000
Give me the money.

147
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,360
What about Huilian?

148
00:06:21,759 --> 00:06:22,759
Who are you looking down on?

149
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,279
Just take it.

150
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:25,240
Keep it on you.

151
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,680
From now on, you're my bro.

152
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:32,079
If you're looking for a bro, count me in too.

153
00:06:32,639 --> 00:06:34,600
My dad got someone to find Auntie a good spot.

154
00:06:35,079 --> 00:06:35,839
Don't worry.

155
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:56,279
Brother Hai

156
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,920
Let this necklace be our proof

157
00:07:00,399 --> 00:07:01,160
From this day on

158
00:07:01,639 --> 00:07:03,040
we're sworn brothers

159
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:05,279
True brothers, in our hearts

160
00:07:05,279 --> 00:07:06,160
In our hearts

161
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,120
And you?

162
00:07:09,319 --> 00:07:10,399
Who'd be brothers with you?

163
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:19,120
True brothers, for life

164
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,079
Agreed

165
00:07:31,879 --> 00:07:32,279
Forget it

166
00:07:33,199 --> 00:07:35,079
Looks like I can't pull off this mission

167
00:07:35,879 --> 00:07:36,519
Mission?

168
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:38,160
So you really do have a mission

169
00:07:38,399 --> 00:07:38,800
Talk

170
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:40,839
Spit it out

171
00:07:42,519 --> 00:07:44,120
Ge Zhendong sent me

172
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,480
He told me to drive a wedge

173
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,839
between you and Zhu Yihai

174
00:07:48,160 --> 00:07:49,680
Who knew you two were this close?

175
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,600
Ge Zhendong?

176
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:52,879
No way

177
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:54,040
You think I'm stupid?

178
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:54,959
You got any proof?

179
00:07:54,959 --> 00:07:56,480
Believe me or not

180
00:07:57,199 --> 00:07:58,639
everything I'm saying is true

181
00:07:58,959 --> 00:08:01,480
I know all the dirty stuff Ge Zhendong's done

182
00:08:03,399 --> 00:08:04,040
The proof

183
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,600
is at the head of the guesthouse bed

184
00:08:06,879 --> 00:08:07,959
The evidence is all there

185
00:08:08,639 --> 00:08:09,800
Every bit of it

186
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,360
The truth you're looking for

187
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:12,639
you can go grab it anytime

188
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:15,439
But I have one request

189
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,720
You've gotta promise me

190
00:08:18,319 --> 00:08:20,000
Don't tell Yihai, okay?

191
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:21,839
My feelings for him are real

192
00:08:22,279 --> 00:08:23,600
Yihai's been through enough

193
00:08:23,959 --> 00:08:25,639
Don't drag him into this too, okay?

194
00:08:26,399 --> 00:08:27,600
I'm begging you, Brother Xiong

195
00:08:28,519 --> 00:08:29,279
Brother Xiong

196
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:33,799
They all say Xiong Dali's got no brains

197
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:36,159
But right now I feel scary smart

198
00:08:38,279 --> 00:08:38,600
Brother Xiong

199
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,679
Brother Hai, watch me handle this one

200
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:40,480
Brother Xiong

201
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:55,240
You're here

202
00:08:55,919 --> 00:08:56,519
Where's Dali?

203
00:08:58,399 --> 00:08:58,919
Talk

204
00:09:00,279 --> 00:09:01,159
I don't know

205
00:09:01,759 --> 00:09:03,159
Didn't Xiong Dali say

206
00:09:03,399 --> 00:09:05,360
he was prepping some surprise for you?

207
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:07,840
Surprise?

208
00:09:11,559 --> 00:09:12,120
We've got trouble, Huilian

209
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:12,399
Let's go

210
00:09:14,559 --> 00:09:15,759
Drive safe, okay?

211
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,000
Where are we headed?

212
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,519
Jing'an Guesthouse

213
00:09:26,799 --> 00:09:27,600
Got it
